.SH "NAME"
\fBgit\-snapshot\fR \- create a snapshot of the changes in a dirty working directory
.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
\fBgit snapshot\fR [(\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR)] [(\-m|\-\-message) \fImessage\fR]
.
.br
\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~[\-\- \fIfile\fR [\fIfile\fR \.\.\.]]
